Diagram PNGs on Volusion: /v/vspfiles/sectional-diagrams/{Style}-SC-{code}.png

Source files live in this folder in Git (commit them after regenerating) so CI deploy can mirror them to Volusion with the rest of vspfiles/.

Regenerate from Palliser Product Summary PDFs (auto crop, 300 DPI default):
  tools/sectional-diagrams/export_diagrams.ps1
or:  python tools/sectional-diagrams/export_sectional_diagrams.py --publish

When adding a NEW style: add rows in vspfiles/js/sectional-configs.js + one palliser block in tools/sectional-diagrams/catalog.json, run export, commit the new PNGs here.
